NASDAQ listing doesn’t change it fundamentally, but gives it more liquidity to bridge that valuation gap.

Next year $10B very possible on

text:
@ravietweet Morgan Stanley now ended up holding 6.5% of $SOI, which was my other silicon photonics long.

I’m do show retail the structural chokepoints in AI before institutions figure it out… 

Point72, $MTSI and others ended up buying $IQE float after my thesis post too.

@aleabitoreddit $GOOGL was incredibly impressive

super excited for photonics and $NBIS

not worried about $META AH drop personally

